     H            Y.
     F** UTLR33B  ****************************************************
     F*  PROGRAM    : GET PART WEIGHT                                *
     F*  WRITTEN    : JW  2024.04.16                                 *
     F*--------------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR33B'
     F*                    PARM           $IPAR  12
     F*                    PARM           $NONY   4
     F*                    PARM           $NET    7
     F*                    PARM           $MSC    7
     F*   IN  $IPAR : 12A IAF PART#
     F*       $NONY :  4A DELIVERY#  (BLANK: COMMON PART)
     F*   OUT $NET  :  7A NET WEIGHT (7, 2)
     F*       $MSC  :  7A MISC. (PALLET..)
     F****************************************************************
     FFCEPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
      *---------------------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1  12 K#SHIN
     I                                        1   5 K#SHN1
     I                                        6  10 K#SHN2
     I                                       11  12 K#SHN3
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      ******************************************************
      *                    MAIN PROCESS
      ******************************************************
     C                     EXSR #INIT
      *
     C           KEY1      CHAINFCEPL01              98
     C           *IN98     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     Z-ADDA2KASI    @NET
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE @NET      $NET
     C                     MOVE @MSC      $MSC
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      *****************************************
      * INITIAL SETTING
      *****************************************
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $IPAR  12
     C                     PARM           $NONY   4
     C                     PARM           $NET    7
     C                     PARM           $MSC    7
      *
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K#SHN1  5
     C                     KFLD           K#SHN2  5
     C                     KFLD           K#SHN3  2
      *
     C                     MOVEL$IPAR     K#SHIN
      *
     C           $NONY     IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     Z-ADD0         @NONY   40
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVEL$NONY     @NONY
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ZEROS    $NET
     C                     MOVE *ZEROS    $MSC
     C                     Z-ADD0         @NET    72
     C                     Z-ADD0.3       @MSC    72
      *
     C                     ENDSR
